snippet.title: Wonder Wickets: Music and Sound (Beta)
snippet.description:
Finally! Featuring official music and sounds for Wonder Wickets!

Music by https://stijnvanwakeren.bandcamp.com/
SFX by http://www.fatbard.com/

The music is made of 3 layers, and each layer plays at different volumes, depending the actions/mood, with emphasis on certain layers.

Not all of the sound effects and music are made/implemented yet, and we'll have more soon.
